Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: PyDisdrometer
Version: 0.1.5
Summary: Pyton Disdrometer Processing
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/PyDisdrometer/
Author: Joseph C. Hardin
Author-email: josephhardinee@gmail.com
License: LICENSE.txt
Description: PyDisdrometer is a Python package to process disdrometer files. It currently is capable of reading several different types of disdrometers and calculating both important moment parameters, as well as radar derived parameters. It currently supports OTT Parsivel disdrometers and Joss Waldvogel Disdrometers. It is currently in alpha so functionality is limited but being expanded quickly..
        
        Author: Joseph C. Hardin
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
Classifier: Development Status :: 3 - Alpha
Classifier: Environment :: Console
